---
import ServicePage from '../../components/ServicePage.astro';
---
<ServicePage
	title="in Clapham"
	highlight="Podiatry"
	heroSubtitle="Podiatry and chiropody care that looks beyond the foot — resolving pain, restoring movement, and keeping the problem from coming back."
	breadcrumb="Podiatry"
	seoTitle="Podiatry in Clapham"
	seoDescription="Podiatry and chiropody in Clapham. Expert care for heel pain, Achilles, orthotics, running injuries, nails, and skin — integrated with the Balance team."
	intro={[
		"If your feet aren\'t working well, nothing above them will either. Foot and ankle problems don\'t stay local. They affect how you move, how you load your joints, and often show up as pain elsewhere — in the knees, hips, or lower back.",
		"Our podiatry and chiropody service focuses on understanding that link. We look at how your body interacts with the ground, and how that influences everything above it.",
		"The aim is simple: resolve pain, restore movement, and make sure the problem doesn\'t come back.",
	]}
	whenHeading="When to consider"
	whenHighlight="podiatry"
	whenIntro="Common reasons people see us:"
	whenList={[
		"Heel pain, including plantar fasciitis",
		"Achilles pain or stiffness",
		"Neuroma or forefoot pain",
		"Shin pain or running-related injuries",
		"Recurrent ankle sprains or instability",
		"Changes in walking or running pattern",
		"Knee, hip, or back pain linked to how you move",
		"Concerns about a child\'s foot development or gait",
		"Considering off-the-peg or custom insoles",
		"Corns, calluses, ingrown toenails, verrucas, fungal nails, or cracked heels",
	]}
	howHeading="How we"
	howHighlight="treat"
	howIntro="Assessment and treatment are tailored to the cause, not just the site of pain."
	howList={[
		"Detailed biomechanical and gait assessment",
		"Diagnostic ultrasound where it helps clarify diagnosis",
		"Orthotic prescription when clinically appropriate",
		"Nail and skin care for chiropody conditions",
		"Joint sessions with physiotherapists, strength coaches, or running specialists",
		"Clear loading and footwear advice to keep the problem from returning",
	]}
	whoHeading="Who we"
	whoHighlight="help"
	whoList={[
		"Runners and athletes with foot, ankle, or lower limb injuries",
		"People with chronic heel, Achilles, or forefoot pain",
		"Patients seeking advice on footwear and orthotics",
		"Children with developmental or gait concerns",
		"Anyone with nail or skin conditions affecting the feet",
	]}
	faqs={[
		{ q: "What\'s the difference between a podiatrist and a chiropodist?", a: "The terms are often used interchangeably, but podiatry reflects a more modern, biomechanical approach to foot and lower limb health." },
		{ q: "Do I need orthotics?", a: "Not always. We only prescribe them where they\'re clinically appropriate." },
		{ q: "Can you help with running injuries?", a: "Yes — we assess how you move and load, not just the site of pain." },
		{ q: "Is ultrasound included?", a: "Only where needed. It can be added to your assessment if it helps clarify your diagnosis." },
		{ q: "Can you assess children?", a: "Yes — we offer paediatric assessments for development and gait concerns." },
	]}
/>
